snippet.title: Game Boy Advance - Crayon Shin-Chan - Densetsu o Yobu Omake no Miyako Shukkugaan! © 2006 Banpresto
snippet.description:
DESCRIPTION
Crayon Shin-Chan: Densetsu o Yobu Omake no Miyako Shukkugaan! is an Action game, developed by Inti Creates and published by Banpresto, which was released in Japan in 2006.
